# mojo-package-build-and-distribution — History

## v1.0.0 (2026-06-07)

Initial canonical skill, merged from 3 source skills:

- `architecture-shipping-mojo-package-prefix-dev` (architecture, v2.0.0)
- `phase-package` (tooling, v1.0.0)
- `ci-package-workflow` (ci-cd, v2.0.0)

The merged skill consolidates Mojo library packaging (`.mojopkg` build, idiomatic
`src/<pkg>/` layout), conda-channel distribution via rattler-build + modular-community
org-fork PR workflow, the Python wheel options, the distribution-channel decision matrix,
and GitHub Actions automation for building and releasing `.mojopkg` artifacts.

